claim.claim-text:
1. A system comprises: a handheld device, including: a computing device; a keypad: and an image input device for acquiring images;
the computing device configured to: send a representation of at least one acquired image; and send a navigation command based on user entries made on the keypad; and
an external, remote computing system communicating with the handheld device, the external, remote computing system configured to: receive the representation of the acquired image: perform at least one processing function on the received representation of the image to provide a result that is processed according to the navigation command; and send the result processed according to the navigation command to the handheld device.

8. A handheld device comprises:
an image input device for acquiring images;
a keypad;
circuitry to determine user navigation commands from user entered data from the keypad;
circuitry to send a representation of at least one image acquired by the image input device to an external, remote computing system that performs at least one processing function related to processing of the image and to send the navigation commands; and
circuitry to receive from the external, remote computing system, data based on processing of the image by the external remote system that provides a result that is processed by the external, remote computing system according to the navigation commands.
